Class BuildYourOwn

java.lang.Object
com.pizza_group.project4.Pizza
com.pizza_group.project4.BuildYourOwn
All Implemented Interfaces:
Customizable
public class BuildYourOwn extends Pizza implements Customizable
BuildYourOwn class handles all BuildYourOwn pizza specific operations in relation to setting the size price, add/removing toppings, and calculating price.
Author:
Alexis Wilson, James Alba
